      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "GOT A PUNCH (7) looks close to win after hitting the frame last run (23.07) at this track in a Grade 5. Has first look at box 7 this time. Has never been out of the money in three starts this distance. Well-placed to take this out. AUSSIE RUSH (5) is rarely out of the finish, recording 11 places from 21 starts. Has hit the frame the last two runs, the latest when third (23.26) at this track. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings four times from five starts. Racing well and deserves a win. GOT A SPORT (1) was prominent early from the tricky draw and did a fair job to be beaten 3.5 lengths into third (22.38) at Shepparton in a Mix 6/7 over 390m. Expected to feature. SYCAMORE SHORTY (2) is worth another chance despite missing the top-three here most recently.",
